description: Build sections from data/* only; no hardcoded content
globs: "**/*.tsx,app/**"
alwaysApply: false
---

# Section Builder

- Sections and page content must come from `data/` only: me.ts, projects.ts, skills.ts.
- Projects: support status `draft` | `published`; render only items with `status === "published"`.
- Never hardcode project cards, copy, or list items in JSX; always derive from data.
